data.description:
Charming 3 bedroom, 1 bath, large utility room, large primary bedroom and large closet, cute kitchen with window seat, butcher block countertops. Great shade trees in front. 2021 new windows, water heater, 40 year roof, heating and cooling system replaced and electric panel. Conveniently located to lake and highway. This property has 2 storage sheds on a large city lot. 

BRING AN OFFER!!
